configuration.name: config.queries
value:
UPDATE tsopdev.pa_parking_inout_event
SET
  out_vehicle_datetime = '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp,
  parking_status = '${record:value('/eventName')}',
  parking_time_min = EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM ('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime)) / 60,
  parking_time = CASE
        WHEN TRUNC(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM ('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime)) / 3600) < 10
            THEN TO_CHAR(('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime), 'HH24')
            ELSE TRUNC(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM ('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime)) / 3600)::TEXT
    END || ':' ||
    TO_CHAR(('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime), 'MI') || ':' ||
    TO_CHAR(('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime), 'SS'),
  parking_datetime = '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp,
  out_event_id = '${record:value('/eventId')}',
  audit_datetime = TO_TIMESTAMP(${record:value('/eventTime')} / 1000.0)
WHERE
  tenant_id = '${record:value('/tenantId')}'
  AND bld_id = '${record:value('/buildingIdNew')}'
  AND in_vehicle_datetime IS NOT NULL
  AND out_vehicle_datetime IS NULL
  AND vehicle_num = '${record:value('/vehicleNumber')}'
  AND parking_status = '입차'

configuration.name: config.queries
value:
UPDATE tsopdev.pa_parking_inout_event
SET
  out_vehicle_datetime = '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp,
  parking_status = '출차',
  parking_time_min = EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM ('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime)) / 60,
  parking_time = CASE
        WHEN TRUNC(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM ('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime)) / 3600) < 10
            THEN TO_CHAR(('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime), 'HH24')
            ELSE TRUNC(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM ('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime)) / 3600)::TEXT
    END || ':' ||
    TO_CHAR(('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime), 'MI') || ':' ||
    TO_CHAR(('${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp - in_vehicle_datetime), 'SS'),
  parking_datetime = '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp,
  out_event_id = '${record:value('/eventId')}',
  audit_datetime = TO_TIMESTAMP(${record:value('/eventTime')} / 1000.0)
WHERE
  tenant_id = '${record:value('/tenantId')}'
  AND bld_id = '${record:value('/buildingIdNew')}'
  AND parking_datetime < '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp
  AND vehicle_num = '${record:value('/vehicleNumber')}'
  AND parking_status = '입차'
  AND in_vehicle_datetime IS NOT NULL
  AND out_vehicle_datetime IS NULL;

INSERT INTO tsopdev.pa_parking_inout_event
(
  tenant_id
  , bld_id
  , parking_site_id
  , parking_status
  , vehicle_num
  , in_vehicle_datetime
  , parking_datetime
  , in_event_id
)
VALUES
(
  '${record:value('/tenantId')}'
  , '${record:value('/buildingIdNew')}'
  , '${record:value('/parkingSiteId')}'
  , '${record:value('/eventName')}'
  , '${record:value('/vehicleNumber')}'
  , '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp
  , '${record:value('/eventDateTime')}'::timestamp
  , '${record:value('/eventId')}'
);
